Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Act and Essence
By: Marsilio Ficino
---
Since we exercise virtues falsely, but vices actually, we shall become
falsely happy and actually miserable in so far as we ourselves are
concerned. This is what Democritus laughed at. what Heraclitus
deplored, what Socrates desired to cure, and what God can cure.
